    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or as a major project. The engine currently runs but exhibits a consistent knock, and the transmission struggles with gear transitions, indicating an imminent need for repair. Externally, there is significant rust through the wheel wells and rocker panels, along with extensive paint failure and multiple dents. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and several non-functional electronic components, including the radio and power windows. This car will require a substantial investment in time and money to become roadworthy again.",
      "price": 7500.0,
